type TRSLobbyWorlds
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

The type representing the worlds interface in the RS lobby.
*)
type
  TRSLobbyWorlds = record(TRSLobby)
    lobbyID: integer;
    worlds: array of __TRSWorld;
